\c 17
\s Muporofita Eria anoraramiswa naJehovha parukova rwaKeriti
\p
\v 1 Zvino Eria muTishibhi wevagari veGiriyadhi wakati kuna Ahabhi: \add Na\add*Jehovha mupenyu, Mwari waIsraeri\x + 17.12. 18.10,15. 22.14. 2 Madz. 3.14. 5.16. Rut. 3.13.\x*, wandimire pamberi pake\x + 18.15. Det. 10.8.\x*, hapangavi nedova kana mvura\x + Jak. 5.17.\x* makore ano, kunze kwekuti zvaenderana neshoko rangu\x + 18.1.\x*.
\v 2 Shoko raJehovha ndokusvika kwaari richiti:
\v 3 Ibva pano, iwe utendeukire kumabvazuva, uye uzvivanze parukova Keriti rwuri mberi kwaJoridhani.
\v 4 Zvino zvichaitika, uchanwa parukova; uye ndaraira makunguvo kukuriritira ipapo.
\v 5 Naizvozvo wakaenda ndokuita zvinoenderana neshoko raJehovha; nokuti wakaenda ndokugara parukova Keriti rwuri mberi kwaJoridhani.
\v 6 Zvino makunguvo akamuvigira chingwa nenyama mangwanani, uye chingwa nenyama madekwani; ndokunwa parukova.
\v 7 Zvino zvakaitika pakupera kwemazuva kuti rukova rwakapwa; nokuti kwaiva kusina mvura panyika.
\s Muporofita Eria anotumwa kuchirikadzi paZarefati
\p
\v 8 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwaari richiti:
\v 9 Simuka, uende kuZarefati riri reZidhoni, ugogarapo\x + Obh. 20.\x*; tarira, ndaraira mukadzi chirikadzi ipapo kukuriritira.
\v 10 Zvino wakasimuka ndokuenda kuZarefati\x + Obh. 20.\x*. Paakasvika pasuwo reguta, tarira, mukadzi chirikadzi waivapo achiunganidza huni\x + Num.. 15.32,33.\x*. Zvino wakadana kwaari ndokuti: Nditorerei henyu mvura shoma mumukombe ndinwe.
\v 11 Paaienda kunoitora, wakamudana ndokuti: Ndivigirei henyu chimedu chechingwa muruoko rwenyu.
\v 12 Zvino wakati: \add Na\add*Jehovha Mwari wenyu mupenyu\x + 17.12. 18.10,15. 22.14. 2 Madz. 3.14. 5.16. Rut. 3.13.\x*, handina keke, asi ruoko rwuzere rweupfu mudenhe, nemafuta mashoma muchinu; zvino tarirai, ndiri kuunganidza\x + Num.. 15.32,33.\x* huni mbiri, kuti ndipinde ndizvigadzirire ini nemwanakomana wangu, kuti tidye tigofa\x + Isa. 17.6. Jer. 3.14.\x*.
\v 13 Eria ndokuti kwaari: Usatya; enda uite zvinoenderana neshoko rako; asi ndiitire pakutanga keke diki nazvo, ubudisire kwandiri; uye shure kwaizvozvo uchazviitira iwe nemwanakomana wako.
\v 14 Nokuti ndizvo zvinoreva Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri: Denhe reupfu haringapedzwi, uye chinu chemafuta hachingashaiwi, kusvika pazuva Jehovha raachapa mvura pachiso chenyika.
\v 15 Zvino wakaenda ndokuita zvaienderana neshoko raEria; zvino vakadya iye pamwe naye neimba yake mazuva \add mazhinji\add*.
\v 16 Denhe reupfu harina kupedzwa uye chinu chemafuta hachina kushaiwa, zvichienderana neshoko raJehovha raakataura neruoko rwaEria.
\p
\v 17 Zvino zvakaitika shure kwezvinhu izvi \add kuti \add*mwanakomana wemukadzi mwene weimba wakarwara; uye urwere hwake hwairwadza kwazvo kusvika kusina kusara mweya maari.
\v 18 Zvino \add mukadzi\add* wakati kuna Eria: Ndinei nemwi\x + 2 Sam. 16.10. Ruk. 5.8.\x*, munhu waMwari\x + Vato. 13.6.\x*? Makapinda mumba mangu kuti chivi changu chirangarirwe, uye kuuraya mwanakomana wangu here\x + Num.. 5.15.\x*?
\v 19 Zvino wakati kwaari: Ndipe mwanakomana wako. Zvino wakamutora kubva pachifuva chake ndokumukwidza muimba yepamusoro maaigara, ndokumuradzika pamubhedha wake\x + 17.23.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino wakadanidzira kuna Jehovha ndokuti: Jehovha Mwari wangu, mawisira chakaipawo kumukadzi wandakava mweni pamwe naye nekuuraya mwanakomana wake here\x + 2 Madz. 4.33,34,35.\x*?
\v 21 Zvino wakatsivama pamusoro pemwana katatu, ndokudanidzira kuna Jehovha, ndokuti: Jehovha Mwari wangu, mweya wemwana uyu ngaudzokere hawo mukati make\x + 2 Madz. 4.33,34,35.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino Jehovha wakanzwa inzwi raEria; mweya wemwana ndokudzokera mukati make, akararamazve\x + VaHeb. 11.35.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino Eria wakatora mwana ndokumuburusa kubva muimba yekumusoro ndokuenda mumba ndokumupa kuna mai vake. Eria ndokuti: Onai, mwanakomana wenyu mupenyu\x + 17.23.\x*.
\v 24 Mukadzi ndokuti kuna Eria: Ikozvino ndinoziva\x + Joh. 3.2; 16.30.\x* ichi, kuti muri munhu waMwari, uye shoko raJehovha riri mumuromo menyu nderechokwadi\x + Vato. 13.6.\x*.